data.description: Professionally updated and completely refreshed extra large home in a great location. The moment you enter from the quaint covered country front porch you will be struck by the wonderful open concept and the amazing light.  Expansive LVP floors throughout main, new countertops in the big kitchen, gorgeous white cabinets, dining area w/new slider leading to the back patio and a fully fenced private yard. Freshly painted big bright rooms soothe the soul. Nice sized den and a convenient 1/2 bath complement the first floor. Upstairs you will find 4 lg bedrooms to include the elegant primary suite w/his & her closets, a new double vanity. Thick new carpeting on stairs and entire second floor. 2" blinds on windows. Nice big garage with storage.
